{"tid":1170691,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"而家啲小朋友真係慘 ，CCTVB星期六晏晝都冇嘢好睇","createTime":"2019-05-25T07:28:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T06:45:40.000Z","uid":34471,"like":168,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"8b58ff5d9913772af68632efb49a5919c8a49bc2","tid":1170691,"uid":34471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:28:51.000Z","msg":"1530-1630 第十三屆香港盃外交知識競[普]<br />\n外交知識邊有興趣知啊，仲要係蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n1630-1700 Big Big小明星<br />\n九成九細路都唔會對呢啲真人自high嘅節目有興趣啦，悶到抽筋。真係貪隻patrick sir靚仔咩on9<br />\n<br />\n1700-1730 爆趣pin碼<br />\n知識紀錄片，到咗禮拜六都仲要學嘢，平時明珠台嗰啲大把啦<br />\n<br />\n1730-1800 櫻桃小丸子<br />\n呢個好少少，但唔算吸引<br />\n<br />\n1800-1830 大自然的日常<br />\n又係知識紀錄片，一個晏晝播兩個咁嘅節目<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話咩生活模式改變令收視變低<br />\n呢啲節目放返喺十幾廿年前，我都寧願打機或者出街玩啦<br />\n小朋友難得禮拜六日放假，點會浪費時間睇呢啲垃圾<br />\n諗到播呢啲節目嘅人真係腦殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba857a1c50dd2e393230a6e88babbf7f660591d3","tid":1170691,"uid":99642,"like":11,"dislike":18,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T07:39:17.000Z","msg":"鬼得閒睇電視劇咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多班要上<br />\n<br />\n又要去公園玩<br />\n<br />\n又就黎考試"},{"pid":"758af5fc04a7e9339ba6ed3ad6b79dcee0c2ec08","tid":1170691,"uid":143621,"like":33,"dislike":14,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-25T08:07:56.000Z","msg":"依個年代仲睇tvb 就真係慘啦 智力正常都唔睇中共大台啦<br />\n<br />\n樓豬仲咁有心list out啲節目 有冇晚晚追埋佢啲新聞一路睇一路講中國係最大贏家啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1e3c28e1998fca7cf976d753ed2471054536f65","tid":1170691,"uid":131621,"like":54,"dislike":0,"score":54,"citedBy":2,"rep